    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Un ta KUNGA Engelis\nfazzija us to : Es wairodams wai-\nroschu tawu Dsimmumu / ta/ ka\ntas preekfch leela Pulka ne taps\nskaitihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Un ta KUNGA Engelis\nfazzija us to : Redsi/ tu efi grub-\ntena/ un dsemdest Dehtu/ un ne-\nfauksi winna Wahrdnu Ismaēls/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "12. Un tas buhs weens War-\nwehrse/ winna Rohka buhs pret\nwisfeem/ un ikkatra Rohka pret\nwinnu/ un wiꞥsch dsihwohs wi-\njeem fatweem Brahtein prettibā\n"
