      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Un Ahgare dsemdeja Ah-\nbramam weenu Dehtu / un Ah-\nbrams nosaunze fawa Dehta Wah-\ndu/ ko tam Ahgare bij dsemdeju\nfi Ismaēls.\n"
